## 🌍 Free Deployment

You can deploy this API for free using:

* Render (recommended)
* Railway
* Fly.io
* Ngrok (Port Forwarding)
* Cloudflare (Port Forwarding)

## ⚠️ Limitations

* OCR accuracy depends on image quality
* May detect any 12-digit number as Aadhaar
* First API call is slow (model download)
* Large PDFs increase processing time

---

## 🚀 Future Improvements

* Aadhaar validation using Verhoeff algorithm
